gemma2.reason: Multiple sources state that Martin Hellman was a professor at Stanford who supervised Ralph Merkle, Whitfield Diffie, and Taher Elgamal as doctoral students.

llama3.1.reason: The claim is wrong because Martin Hellman was the supervisor of Ralph Merkle, not the other way around.

qwen2.5.reason: Martin Hellman was a professor at Stanford through 1996 and had doctoral students himself, including Ralph Merkle. He could not have been a doctoral student of Ralph Merkle.
